home.name: Brisbane Broncos
home.comments: FINAL TEAM: Once again Herman Ese'ese and Alex Glenn move into the starting side with Korbin Sims and Sam Thaiday moving back to the bench. Jordan Kahu returns on the wing with David Mead moving back to the interchange.

away.name: Penrith Panthers
away.comments: FINAL TEAM: Viliame Kikau replaces Moses Leota on the Panthers bench in their only change.

title: South Sydney Rabbitohs vs Manly Warringah Sea Eagles

home.name: South Sydney Rabbitohs
home.comments: FINAL TEAM: The Rabbitohs are 1-17. Adam Reynolds returns while John Sutton returns to the forward pack with George Burgess out with a four-game suspension.

title: North Queensland Cowboys vs Parramatta Eels

home.name: North Queensland Cowboys
home.comments: FINAL TEAM: Johnathan Thurston remains on the sidelines for the Cowboys with Ray Thompson replacing Blake Leary at hooker and Ben Hampton joining the bench.

away.name: Parramatta Eels
away.comments: FINAL TEAM: Will Smith comes into the side at five-eighth with Kenny Edwards moving back to the bench.

title: Gold Coast Titans vs Newcastle Knights

home.name: Gold Coast Titans
home.comments: Updated Titans: Dale Copley, Chris Grevsmuhl and Karl Lawton are all out injured. Tyronne Roberts-Davis returns to the backline and Kane Elgey and Pat Vaivai join the bench. Pat Politoni and Alex Brimson drop out.

away.name: Newcastle Knights
away.comments: Updated Knights: Jaelen Feeney comes into the starting side at halfback, with Sione Mata'utia returning to the second row. Luke Yates starts at lock for the injured Mitchell Barnett. Joe Wardle returns on the bench. Pauli Pauli and Lachlan Fitzgibbon drop out.

title: Canterbury Bankstown Bulldogs vs Canberra Raiders

home.name: Canterbury Bankstown Bulldogs
home.comments: FINAL TEAM: Will Hopoate comes into the Bulldogs side at fullback, with Adam Elliot starting in the second row, Greg Eastwood back to the interchange and Matt Frawley starting on the bench. Raymond Faitala-Mariner and Marcelo Montoya drop out.

away.name: Canberra Raiders
away.comments: FINAL TEAM: Luke Bateman starts at lock for Canberra with Joseph Tapine dropping back to the bench in their only change.

title: Wests Tigers vs Cronulla Sutherland Sharks

home.name: Wests Tigers
home.comments: FINAL TEAM: Tim Grant has been ruled out with a shoulder injury, with JJ Felise joining the interchange bench.

away.name: Cronulla Sutherland Sharks
away.comments: Updated Sharks: Luke Lewis has been ruled out with a hamstring injury, replaced by Tony Williams who will make his Sharks debut. Gerard Beale returns on the wing, pushing Kurt Capewell to the bench.

title: New Zealand Warriors vs Sydney Roosters

home.name: New Zealand Warriors
home.comments: FINAL TEAM: The Warriors are 1-17. Charnze Nicoll-Klokstad will make his NRL debut, named to replace Solomone Kata. Manu Vatuvei and Albert Vete drop out of the initial 21-man squad.

away.name: Sydney Roosters
away.comments: FINAL TEAM: The Roosters have made a couple of changes with Aidan Guerra starting in the second row, pushing Mitchell Aubusson to the bench. Sio Siua Taukeiaho starts at lock with Connor Watson coming on to the bench. Paul Carter drops out of the side.

title: St George Illawarra Dragons vs Melbourne Storm

away.name: Melbourne Storm
away.comments: FINAL TEAM: The Storm have made one change with Joe Stimson playing on the bench, with Ryley Jacks dropping out.
